==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: kangaroo rat
<hw>kangaroo rat</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>A jumping
rodent of the genus <gen>Dipodomys</gen> of the family
<fam>Heteromyidae</fam>, which lives in arid regions of Mexico and the
western U. S.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>An Australian mammal of the genus
<gen>Notomys</gen>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><sn>3.</sn> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>a small ratlike Australian
kangaroo of the genus <gen>Potorous</gen>, also called the
<altname>potoroo</altname>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>kangaroo's-foot</ent>⟦br⟧
